overview:
Jorbb.com (http://jorbb.com) is Singaporeâ€™s newest site created expressly for non-executive jobs, for individuals seeking freelance, contract, part-time and casual employment. This innovative and uniquely interactive portal enables its users to not only post their resumes, but also photos, slideshows and video profiles.

Jorbbers (Employers) can receive applications and make their decisions based on the Jorbbees (Job Seekers) character analysis surveys. Users also have the opportunity to rate each other and post testimonials for the benefit of future users.

In an overcrowded market dominated by expensive executive job search sites, Jorbb.comâ€™s design and interface offer something refreshing. With 1st Ad Posting Free and subsequent posts at only S$25, Job Ads specific to a Jorbbeeâ€™s interested job categories are sent to him/her directly via Email / RSS feeds, so Jorbbers get targeted traffic to their ads.

Users can earn credits which can be exchanged for exciting gifts such as featured listings, movie tickets, vouchers and gadgets. Simply refer a friend, post a testimonial or rate Jorbbers or Jorbbees. Bloggers can also reap rewards by posting about the site or suggesting improvements.

Finding that freelance, contract, part-time or casual job is quick with Visual Search - an innovative map search feature assisting users in their pursuit for posted jobs / jobs eekers in their desired locations and even provides travel directions.

Jorbb.com will actively seek partnerships with other local Web 2.0 sites. For a start, Jorbb.com will partner with Gothere.sg to leverage its public transport and commuting data.
